{"tid":1101144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(焦土派)洛杉磯僑胞: 韓國瑜出選總統, 我們一定回台灣投票","createTime":"2019-04-11T00:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T23:14:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc79d7c70114a5c6f587d3fb4dc026ef6a9bb5f","tid":1101144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"又係中時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190410001541-260407?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190410001541-260407%3Fchdtv&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=aeabcb4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190410001541-260407?chdtv</a> <br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜引爆「韓流」，聲勢驚人！本尊仍在赴美飛機上，韓粉卻如千千萬萬分身，早已遍地開花，著自製T恤聚集洛杉磯，準備讓韓一下機就感受世界各地台灣人最深切的盼望！ <br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯僑胞們一見記者，迫不及待揮舞國旗，高喊「選總統，救台灣」、「台灣安全，人民有錢」！不只如此，僑胞們身上的T恤更是吸睛焦點。「這是你們自己做的嗎？」一聽記者詢問，僑胞們立刻分享自己如何親手繪圖、製版，匯聚心血完成這一件件T恤，激動、驕傲之情溢於言表。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，僑胞們也表示，過去幾年他們已對回台投票冷感，但今年卻大不相同。「只要是韓國瑜，我們一定回去投票！」「只要韓國瑜出來選，我們通通坐飛機回去！」「為了韓國瑜，明年1月一定回台灣投票！」強烈呼喚聲此起彼落，更有人表示，已有上百人登記回台助選，只要是韓出戰他們立刻啟動！ <br />\n<br />\n雖然國民黨內幾顆「太陽」至今喬不定，但基層無論國內外早按捺不住，不惜用各種方式，就是要告訴國民黨中央──非韓勿擾。"},{"pid":"d5da90f8e8bb2b1af38946bfeca22ea9df195291","tid":1101144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8724d8e21d58559a0eb3158d5001baa7480b0c84","tid":1101144,"uid":129,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:42:13.000Z","msg":"賣台報+賣台狗"},{"pid":"f5115a34ce7f79e91c7acda8dc2c03e9606348ea","tid":1101144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8724d8e21d58559a0eb3158d5001baa7480b0c84","tid":1101144,"uid":129,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:42:13.000Z","msg":"賣台報+賣台狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca4b490b6c694575edb436f9f9292987c0c1859","tid":1101144,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:47:56.000Z","msg":"G持韓國瑜代表國民黨參選總統<br />\n台版國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedef67773026ab307189127e9c0cf0f3f527bbc","tid":1101144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aca4b490b6c694575edb436f9f9292987c0c1859","tid":1101144,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:47:56.000Z","msg":"G持韓國瑜代表國民黨參選總統<br />\n台版國師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d4cf77803718cf501a694c74b7dc3139f9bdf4","tid":1101144,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟韓國瑜搬去大灣區啦"},{"pid":"cbe990c6e4e4893a7a9253a94016bd1ce017b2e2","tid":1101144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63d4cf77803718cf501a694c74b7dc3139f9bdf4","tid":1101144,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟韓國瑜搬去大灣區啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a275cc49d24a557e9ad419453ba08210031c43","tid":1101144,"uid":53498,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy